        p Laskin also takes great pride in their new and unique approach to fat loss & body sculpting with low frequency ultrasound technology followed controlled volumetric heating with radio frequency that enables sculpting, lifting and toning of the face and body for the desired look you have always wanted. 

        p Tallking about detoxification, we surely cannot miss the 'angel of water' colon cleansing treatment that gently enhances your inner health by cleansing years of stagnant toxic waste preparing you for a healthy lifestyle. 

